every html element is a box when you  apply a background

box do have four side 1.e top,right,bottom lef.
proprerty to beautify box


!.padding=>this is used apply space within a box

margin=> this applies space outside the box

width=>this controls the dimension 
height=> this is used to control the dimension on the vertrical axis
border=>this apply design to the edges of an html element
outline=. same as border but a layer above border
box-sizing=> shrink box so as to control overall sizing of the box
overflow=> control content inside a box from flowing out

type of positioning:


1. static => default to every element.(i cant move)
relative moves in refeerance to where the element isabsolute=> this can  move to any point in the screen
fixed  calculate like absolute and pin in to a point